pan><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/26/01 11:17:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> JBoots!</span><hr size=1> I still stand by that any horse other than 110K is a waste, if you're getting it purely for speed (and no mana regen reasons) =P <br><br>Heres why:<br>No Levi... I love levi + jboots, great for kiting in CS/TD and travel in many other places.  Sure Horses have safefall, but what good does that do me when i run over water to round stuff up?<br>Horses drop the second you zone in doors.  JBoots you can click right before you zone in and have the speed for a good while longer.  <br>JBoots are instant, horses have a slight delay.  <br><br>I say go for JBoots.<br>If you have cash left over and want a horse for mana regen (regen while running/standing/casting) get a crappy 8K one?  <br><br>My thoughts <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uoxoxoxoxox.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Oxoxo Xoxox</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalRainbow.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/27/01 10:08:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www2.swmed.edu/libraryis/eq/wizsig4.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> jboots or better yet, innate run speed alt xp points</span><hr size=1> Horses are not for soloing/kiting.  What they are for is grouping outdoors and getting places fast.  The Horses kick major ass tho because while grouped outdoors(or in dungeons considered outdoors) you are always considered medding even while moving or casting on one.  <br><br>The 110k horse is a waste of money as well as the 10k horse.  I say this because the 60k horse goes so fast who really cares if your a tad faster. For almost double the price when no one can tell by looking at it? I dont think so.  The 10k horse is slower than jboots and if your gonna spend massive plats on a horse at least get some good speed out of it.<br><br>10k horse - do not buy<br>30k horse - great horse<br>60k horse - best horse<br>110 horse - do not buy unless you like flushing money down the toilet.<br><br>as for comparing Jboots and horses.  forget both if you want a solo/kiting solution.  Get innate run speed x3 alt xp advancement and you will always run at jboots speed indoors and out.  Save you plats for a nice horse 30k/60k<br><br>P.S.  The Horse's safe fall skill is so high you can ride off the Kelethin lifts and only take 200ish damage, anything lower than that and you dont take damage at all <p><b><a href='http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=3693'>Oxoxo Xoxox</a></b> lvl 56 Evoker<BR><b><a href='http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=57344'>Rubix Stumpyshorts</a></b> lvl 30 Cleric <br>Oxoxo Xoxox lvl 17 Lukreen Eldritch<br>Xoxox Oxoxo lvl 24 Lukreen Mentalist<br>Ouji lvl 10 Lukreen Nightshade<br><A HREF="http://www.mithrilweb.com" target="blank"><img src="http://www.queensidecastle.com/eq/Luclinsig.jpg" border="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aksel>Aksel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/28/01 3:23:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: jboots or better yet, innate run speed alt xp points</span><hr size=1> What is this about horses having mana regen? Do they? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulonnc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lonn c</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/28/01 5:40:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.crimsondraconia.com/~lonn/l1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: jboots or better yet, innate run speed alt xp points</span><hr size=1> Oki here what my exp is with horses:<br><br>I myself have a tan chain horse (its the fastes buy able)<br><br>Horses are useless for keiting , since they<br>need to to reach there speed and time to stop.<br><br>If you wanna solo get runspeed 3 or jboots.<br><br>If you wanna buy a horse , save 100k and buy<br>the fastes , all others are a waste.<br>Did a horse race with ppl the others horses , believe me<br>even the 60k isnt worth the cash compared to then 100k<br>one.<br><br>So long Lonn<br>Ghoul Wizard<br>Club FU , Bristlebane<br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://fu-profiles.vestergren.nu/view_player.php?uid=83">fu-profiles.vestergren.nu...php?uid=83</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umalderith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Malderith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/8/02 3:53:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Horse or Jboots</span><hr size=1> This is already posted on the general forum but should be posted here as well.  VI is planning on taking out the med while standing still on the horse.  If you want to quad with them do it for the speed alone b/c the mana regen perk is going away.<br><br>*edit* With new patch they have only said meditating while in combat is taken out.  So scratch this post. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umalderith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Malderith</A> at: 1/8/02 4:06:13 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ureprobus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reprobus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/10/02 4:41:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Horse or Jboots</span><hr size=1> I use both.  I herd with Jboots, then mount the horse when Atol's is stuck and the killing begins.  Has worked really well thus far.<br><br><br>Reprobus Krumb<br>Sorcerer of Ashborne, Karana   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showPrevMessage?topicID=254.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showNextMessage?topicID=254.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=254.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif borde